{"comments":"Surface Height — Z-depth tracking for paint piles and displacement.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nPaint isn't flat. Impasto strokes pile up. Watercolor pools in valleys.\nThe height map tracks z-depth at each point on the surface, enabling:\n- Paint stacking and toppling physics\n- Surface deformation under gravity\n- Displacement mapping for 3D rendering\n- Shadows from paint pile edges\n\n## Height Model\n\n- **0.0**: Canvas surface level\n- **Positive**: Paint above surface (impasto)\n- **Negative**: Depressions in surface (scraping, absorption)\n\n## Stability Threshold\n\nFrom the viscous fluid paper (EUROGRAPHICS 2019):\n- Thick paint can support itself (like honey dipper standing in honey)\n- When height exceeds stability threshold, flow/topple triggers\n- Stability depends on viscosity, surface tension, and gravity\n\n## Dependencies\n- Prelude\n- Data.Array\n- Data.Maybe\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","Height"],"HeightValue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Height.purs","start":[132,1]},"title":"eqHeightValue"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","Height"],"HeightValue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Height.purs","start":[133,1]},"title":"ordHeightValue"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"ann